{"pin":"BB00522","subcodes":[{"code":"BB00522","anchor":"","title":"Du'a Hajat","first_line":"O Lord! Send down Thy mercy upon me, for verily all mercy is Thine.... O Lord! Unto Thee I repair for refuge and toward all Thy signs I set my heart. O Lord! Whether traveling or at home","first_line_orig":"بسم الله الرحمن الرحیم. اللهم انزل علی رحمتک فان لک الرحمة کلها اللهم صل على محمد حبیبک و الانبیآء  ","language":"Ara","word_count":"180","subjects":"@prayer for protection, @trust and reliance in God; turning to Him at all times, @prayer for forgiveness","full_text_parts":["O Lord! Unto Thee I repair for refuge, and toward all Thy signs I set my heart.\nO Lord!  Whether traveling or at home, and in my occupation or in my work, I place my whole trust in Thee.\nGrant me then Thy sufficing help so as to make me independent of all things, O Thou Who art unsurpassed in Thy mercy!\nBestow upon me my portion, O Lord, as Thou pleasest, and cause me to be satisfied with whatsoever Thou hast ordained for me.\nThine is the absolute authority to command."],"translations":[]},{"code":"BB00522DET","anchor":"det","translations":[{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"}]},{"code":"BB00522REF","anchor":"ref","translations":[{"language":"vi","lang_name":"Vietnamese"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"cs","lang_name":"Czech"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ceb","lang_name":"Cebuano"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_nam